OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 21 Mar to Mon 30 Mar
OL,6,FUnder the influence of high pressure
OL,7,Fit will be a settled start to this
OL,8,Fperiod, with most places predominantly
OL,9,Fdry, although the odd shower cannot be
OL,10,Fruled out in the southeast, and some
OL,11,Frain may threaten the extreme north or
OL,12,Fnorthwest. Temperatures will be close
OL,13,Fto or a little above average, although
OL,14,Ffor parts of the south it will feel
OL,15,Fcooler than earlier in the week with a
OL,16,Fbrisk easterly wind starting to
OL,17,Fdevelop. Overall though is spells of
OL,18,Fspring sunshine it should feel quite
OL,19,Fpleasant. How long the settled
OL,20,Fconditions last is less certain with
OL,21,Fsome signals that showers / rain could
OL,22,Freturn later in the period, most
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Flikely to the south.
